column5: Eric Hanans & Jenna Strohmann Type: Party - Night of Mayhem Network: Global Start Time: Saturday, March 28, 2009 at 8:00pm End Time: Sunday, March 29, 2009 at 2:00am Location: Jarvis Community Center Street: James St & Park St Phone: 5194436958 Email: [emailÂ protected] Description Jenna and I are getting married and we want to invite all of you to our Jack and Jill. There will be door prizes every half hour, with a BIG prize at 12am and we also have a pair of LEAF TICKETS for a prize too. (Have to be there to win.) Lots of food, music, games and booze!! $10 tickets are available through us, family members and the bridal party. Also available at the door. Hope everyone can make it!
